reviewText: Bought this as a gift, they luved it! Great price / value ($6.99), a nice family show, happy to support them!
Bought this as a gift, they luved it! I wish there were more episodes on this disc for the price ($9.99) BUT the Raggs are totally worth it! Happy to support them!
Unfortunately, I can only take watching this so many times. My son watches this over and over again. I only give it a 3 because I am sick of watching it.
My kids love this DVD and we have watched it several times. Very entertaining, cute, and educational ! Really encourages music influences.
This dvd is great for kids, lots of dancing and music, plus the colors really attracted my baby, she's one now and prefers Elmo now, Sorry Raggs. But all in all this is a good dvd for kids!!
My grandson loves this! I'm going to have to buy this again because he lost the DVD.

Bought this for our boys, after watching the preview for it about a bazillion times on our Wiggles DVD. They love it -- a nice blend of people dressed in costume and cartoon. The music is catchy and they do a nice job of trying to give their characters some diversity.
I receive this dvd and my daughter love's it she watch it over and over again
Wonderful my 4 year old loves it. She loves to sing and dance to raggs.
I had never seen it before, but my granddaughter loves it. I almost know all the songs and I am 68. She plays it all the time.
My great grand daughter loves Raggs
She loves Raggs  cause she can dance to the music.
